      <hedline>
        <hl1>Water Remedies</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Adam Groothuis letter on July 11 article cites added health benefit of drinking water; drawing</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''For Lifelong Gains, Just Add Water. Repeat.'' (July 11):</p>
        <p>One of the most overlooked benefits of drinking plenty of water every day is this: it forces those of us with sedentary jobs to get off our butts and take several extra trips to the bathroom. Sitting at a keyboard all day can wreak havoc on one's body. The additional bathroom breaks can give much-needed relief to stiff lower backs and tight hamstrings.</p>
        <p>ADAM GROOTHUIS  New York</p>
      </block>
